  "title": "Environmental Control Officer (ECO)",
  "description": "<p>Candidate should be farmiliar with LTA/HDB BTO project requirements.</p>\n<p>Candidate should have work experience in Singapore projects work.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The ECO shall possess a Certificate of Competency in Earth Control Measures (ECM) for Construction Site Personnel.</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Valid ECO licence</li>\n  <li>Valid ECMO licence</li>\n  <li>Farmiliar with GGBS audits</li>\n  <li>Expereince with Safety Campaign and Environemetal Campaign</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The ECO shall compile and submit environmental related data :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Data include water, electricity and diesel consumption on site</li>\n  <li>Concrete wastage on site</li>\n  <li>Amount of constuction debris generated on site</li>\n  <li>Noise and vectors records to NEA</li>\n  <li>ECM records to PUB</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified. </em></p>",
